{
  "texts": [
    "We propose a novel feature extraction module, C2fLEFEM, and replace the C3 module in the original YOLOv5 network with this module to reduce high-frequency noise and increase critical information.",
    "Furthermore, we suggest a new Attentional Receptive Field Block (AMRFB).",
    "This module may broaden the receptive field and assign different attention domains to distinct receptive fields, thus boosting the network's feature extraction ability.",
    "We replaced the SPPF module with the SimSPPF module for faster inference and better feature representation.",
    "Furthermore, we modified the C2fLEFEM feature extraction module into the AMC2fLEFEM module, which extracts features of different scales by incorporating a simple attention module (SimAM) to increase the network's feature learning capacity."
  ]
}